# Google Maps, Drones, and Hezek Riah

## Frage

<p>There are Halachos which restrict a one's ability to see into the yard of their neighbor*. Does the use of Google maps constitute Hezek Riah, since one can use it to see into the backyards of others? Would Google be found Halachically liable to pay for damages if tried in a Beis Din? What are some practical Halachos of flying drones?</p>
<p>Sources:</p>
<p>Admur Nizkei Mamon 11;
Rema 154/3;
Mechaber 357/1 “Hezek Reiyah”;
Tur 157;
Rosh Bava Basra 1;
Bava Basra 2b</p>
